ompanies%20are%20deploying%20the%20technology%20rather%20than%20hiring%20graduates.%20And%20it%20is%20also%20consistent%20with%20what%20business%20leaders%20are%20saying%2C%20with%20'AI'%20now%20a%20synonym%20for%20'cost%20cutting%2C'%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Perkins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Perkins%20argues%20the%20real%20reason%20is%20simply%20the%20normal%20course%20of%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20hiring%20is%20weak%20across%20the%20board.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20economy%20as%20a%20whole%20is%20currently%20experiencing%20recessionary%20levels%20of%20job%20creation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerkins'%20analysis%20shows%20that%20sectors%20with%20higher%20AI%20exposure%20are%20not%20experiencing%20larger%20increases%20in%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20identifies%20three%20main%20drivers%20behind%20the%20hiring%20slowdown%20%E2%80%94%20and%20none%20involve%20automation%20replacing%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20firms%20rapidly%20expanded%20their%20workforces%20during%20the%20post-pandemic%20surge%20and%20are%20now%20normalizing%20head%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20policy%20uncertainty%20has%20made%20businesses%20cautious%20about%20taking%20on%20new%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20Trump-era%20tariffs%20have%20squeezed%20profit%20margins%2C%20prompting%20companies%20to%20push%20for%20more%20output%20from%20existing%20employees%20instead%20of%20hiring%20new%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20leaves%20young%20people%20getting%20squeezed%2C%20but%20the%20good%20news%20is%20that%20net%20employment%20is%20stable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20outlook%20should%20improve%20once%20hiring%20rebounds%2C%20Perkins%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20economy%20reaccelerates%20and%20hiring%20rates%20recover%2C%20new%20entrants'%20employment%20prospects%20should%20improve%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerkins'%20report%20came%20as%20markets%20continue%20to%20assess%20the%20impact%20of%20AI%20technology%20on%20the%20economy%20and%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20analysts%20have%20concluded%20that%20young%20tech%20workers%20seem%20to%20be%20taking%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20impact.%20The%20unemployment%20rate%20for%2020-%20to%2030-year-olds%20in%20tech%20has%20risen%20by%20nearly%203%20percentage%20points%20since%20early%202024%2C%20over%20four%20times%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20overall%20jobless%20rate%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-impact-unemployment-job-loss-young-tech-workers-goldman-sachs-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20August%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Goldman%20warned%20of%20an%20era%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-impact-economy-gdp-jobless-growth-productivity-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejobless%20growth%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20due%20to%20AI%2C%20even%20as%20the%20broader%20economy%20remains%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-impact-jobs-youth-unemployment-hiring-freeze-uncertainty-tariffs-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765172063000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F693650f404d0f0a114f190ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-impact-jobs-youth-unemployment-hiring-freeze-uncertainty-tariffs-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20hiring%20freeze%2C%20not%20AI%2C%20is%20pushing%20youth%20unemployment%20higher%20as%20firms%20pause%20expansion%20amid%20uncertainty%20and%20tariffs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-impact-jobs-youth-unemployment-hiring-freeze-uncertainty-tariffs-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22tit