0usefulness%20and%20truth.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20companies%20are%20prioritizing%20flash%20over%20substance%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-surge-ai-leaked-list-sites-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESurge%20AI's%20%3C%2Fa%3ECEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20worried%20that%20instead%20of%20building%20AI%20that%20will%20actually%20advance%20us%20as%20a%20species%2C%20curing%20cancer%2C%20solving%20poverty%2C%20understanding%20universal%2C%20all%20these%20big%20grand%20questions%2C%20we%20are%20optimizing%20for%20AI%20slop%20instead%2C%26quot%3B%20Edwin%20Chen%20said%20in%20an%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BLenny's%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20basically%20teaching%20our%20models%20to%20chase%20dopamine%20instead%20of%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChen%20founded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-training-companies-startups-2025-9%23surge-ai-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20training%20startup%20Surge%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%20after%20working%20at%20Twitter%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Meta.%20Surge%20runs%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-training-account-selling-market-scam-scale-surge-mercor-facebook-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egig%20platform%20Data%20Annotation%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20says%20it%20pays%20one%20million%20freelancers%20to%20train%20AI%20models.%20Surge%20competes%20with%20data%20labeling%20startups%20like%20Scale%20AI%20and%20Mercor%20and%20counts%20Anthropic%20as%20a%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday's%20podcast%2C%20Chen%20said%20that%20companies%20are%20prioritizing%20AI%20slop%20because%20of%20industry%20leaderboards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20the%20industry%20is%20played%20by%20these%20terrible%20leaderboards%20like%20LMArena%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20popular%20online%20leaderboard%20where%20people%20can%20vote%20on%20which%20AI%20response%20is%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20carefully%20reading%20or%20fact-checking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20skimming%20these%20responses%20for%20two%20seconds%20and%20picking%20whatever%20looks%20flashiest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20literally%20optimizing%20your%20models%20for%20the%20types%20of%20people%20who%20buy%20tabloids%20at%20the%20grocery%20store.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurge-ai-product-manager-data-scientist-startup-hire-edwin-chen-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Surge%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20AI%20labs%20have%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20these%20leaderboards%20because%20they%20can%20be%20asked%20about%20their%20rankings%20during%20sales%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Chen%2C%20research%20scientists%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-benchmark-best-model-compare-meta-openai-deepseek-google-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecriticized%20benchmarks%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20overvaluing%20superficial%20traits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20March%20blog%20post%2C%20Dean%20Valentine%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20AI%20security%20startup%20ZeroPath%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BRecent%20AI%20model%20progress%20feels%20mostly%20like%20bullshit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValentine%20said%20that%20he%20and%20his%20team%20had%20been%20evaluating%20the%20performance%20of%20different%20models%20claiming%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Bsome%20sort%20of%20improvement%26quot%3B%20since%20the%20release%20of%20Anthropic's%203.5%20Sonnet%20in%20June%202024.%20None%20of%20the%20new%20models%20his%20team%20tried%20had%20made%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20difference%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20company's%20internal%20benchmarks%20or%20in%20developers'%20abilities%20to%20find%20new%20bugs%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20might%20hav