.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20ordinary%20school%20day%2C%20I've%20got%20to%20be%20up%20by%20about%206%20a.m.%20The%20commute%20to%20school%20is%20about%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20I%20usually%20spend%20that%20hour%20clearing%20work%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20go%20to%20school%20until%203%20or%204%20p.m.%20But%20every%20single%20lunch%20break%20of%20the%20past%20year%2C%20I've%20spent%20it%20working.%20After%20I'm%20home%2C%20I'm%20entirely%20focused%20on%20startup%20work.%20I'll%20study%20a%20bit%20at%20night%2C%20then%20I%20end%20up%20sleeping%20at%20about%202%20or%203%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8126dc5-69fb-4a4c-85a3-0870f8112fc2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20didn't%20want%20to%20wait%20on%20entrepreneurship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sort%20of%20jumped%20straight%20into%20the%20startup%20space.%20It%20was%20scary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20my%20first%20event%2C%20Singapore%20Tech%20Week%2C%20last%20year.%20It%20taught%20me%20that%20if%20I%20could%20hold%20my%20own%20and%20be%20confident%20in%20a%20solid%20idea%2C%20merit%20speaks%20louder%20than%20any%20labels%20like%20my%20age%2C%20gender%2C%20or%20how%20much%20experience%20I%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20AI%20wave%2C%20we're%20seeing%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-young-founders-ai-gold-rush-to-grow-up-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyounger%20people%20make%20breaks%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20startup%20and%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdropped-out-of-college-ai-founder-sacrifice-trade-off-cancer-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eare%20college%20founders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20wait.%20At%20least%20in%20tech%2C%20it's%20a%20very%20open%20space%2C%20more%20so%20than%20traditional%20sectors%20like%20finance%2C%20where%20you%20have%20to%20get%20your%20college%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20fortunate%20to%20