%20met%20Demario%2C%20I%20was%20planning%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-teachers-wish-they-knew-before-they-started-teaching-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecareer%20in%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20I%20would%20become%20a%20teacher%2C%20then%20a%20principal%2C%20then%20a%20superintendent%2C%20before%20moving%20into%20higher%20education.%20However%2C%20after%20we%20were%20married%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20when%20he%20was%20drafted%20by%20the%20Jets%2C%20and%20we%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20signed%20our%20oldest%20up%20for%20preschool%2C%20but%20it%20never%20lasted%20long.%20People%20would%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20you%20looking%20for%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20realized%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20teacher%20like%20me.%20Because%20of%20my%20background%20in%20education%2C%20I%20had%20structured%20our%20home%20like%20a%20schoolhouse%2C%20setting%20up%20learning%20corners%2C%20without%20even%20realizing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomeschool-kids-travel-the-world-modest-budget-worldschooling-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHomeschooling%20fits%20our%20schedule%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20lifestyle%2C%20but%20it's%20about%20so%20much%20more%20than%20that%3A%20it%20feels%20like%20an%20assignment%20from%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220667d79a-d27b-4ecb-a5a9-7f1020abf40f%5C%22%3EAnother%20teacher%20helps%20me%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20typical%20day%2C%20I%20require%20the%20kids%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bon%26quot%3B%20from%207%20to%207.%20They%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fschool-uniforms-around-the-world-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewear%20uniforms%3C%2Fa%3E%20Monday%20through%20Thursday.%20It's%20a%20way%20of%20teaching%20professional%20development.%20It's%20very%20important%20to%20show%20up%20in%20the%20world%20in%20a%20way%20that%20reflects%20who%20you%20are%2C%20and%20presentation%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20that.%20It's%20almost%20like%20etiquette%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20kids%20are%2012%2C%2010%2C%209%2C%206%2C%204%2C%20and%201%20years%20old.%20We%20have%20a%20very%20individualized%20approach%20to%20learning%2C%20so%20sometimes%20they%20follow%20the%20same%20curriculum%2C%20and%20sometimes%20they%20don't.%20Right%20now%2C%20I%20have%20another%20teacher%20come%20in%20to%20help%3A%20she'll%20work%20with%20the%20big%20kids%20while%20I%20work%20with%20the%20littles%2C%20then%20we'll%20switch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260be4119-22a3-44fc-a6e6-8d1e7e2ae7af%5C%22%3EWe%20want%20the%20kids%20to%20know%20they're%20our%20most%20important%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20game%20days%2C%20we%20get%20up%20early%20and%20have%20doughnuts%20for%20breakfast.%20The%20kids%20lay%20out%20their%20clothes%20the%20night%20before%20and%20complete%20their%20checklist.%20We%20aim%20to%20get%20to%20the%20stadium%20an%20hour%20before%20kickoff.%20The%20kids%20enjoy%20watching%20Dad%2C%20and%20especially%20love%20running%20onto%20the%20field%20with%20him%20after%20the%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20our%20schedule%2C%20family%20dinners%20are%20very%20important%20to%20me.%20We%20typically%20have%20dinner%20together%20at%206%20p.m.%20on%20Mondays%20through%20Thursdays%20during%20the%20season.%20If%20we%20can't%20do%20that%20because%20a%20child%20has%20an%20activity%2C%20we%20find%20time%20to%20gather%20together%20as%20a%20family%20before%20bed.%20We%20use%20video%20chat%20if%20Demario%20is%20traveling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kids%20need%20to%20know%20that%20although%20life%20is%20busy%2C%20they're%20extremely%20important%20to%20us%20and%20they're%20important%20to%20each%20other.%20We%20always%20tell%20them%3A%20we're%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fim-married-to-nfl-player-heres-why-homeschool-our-kids-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22pub