0the%20current%20size%20and%20state%20of%20the%20airlift%20fleet%20may%20not%20meet%20potential%20wartime%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20peer%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warns%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20airlift%20fleet%20may%20not%20be%20sufficient%20to%20meet%20the%20movement%2C%20supply%2C%20and%20other%20logistical%20demands%20of%20the%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20may%20not%20have%20enough%20airlift%20to%20support%20its%20ACE%20concept%2C%26quot%3B%20Owen%20says%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20service's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-war-gamed-pilots-fighting-without-communications-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAgile%20Combat%20Employment%3C%2Fa%3E%20strategy%20aimed%20at%20disaggregating%20assets%20to%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20an%20adversary%20to%20cripple%20US%20airpower%20in%20a%20single%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-china-missile-problem-getting-worse-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoverwhelming%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20fewer%20aircraft%20available%20for%20carrying%20personnel%20and%20equipment%20into%20the%20fight%2C%20and%20the%20ones%20the%20US%20does%20have%20aren't%20the%20right%2C%20varied%20mix%20for%20a%20high-end%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20relies%20heavily%20on%20a%20mix%20of%20C-17s%2C%20converted%20airliners%2C%20and%20helicopters%20to%20haul%20cargo%2C%20refuel%20aircraft%2C%20and%20move%20people%20between%20theaters.%20But%20many%20of%20these%20airframes%20are%20now%20decades%20old%20and%20sliding%20toward%20obsolescence%2C%20Owen%20writes.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20the%20mobility%20fleet%20was%20significantly%20younger%2C%20and%20the%20Pentagon%20had%20clear%20plans%20to%20replace%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20airlift%20aircraft%2C%20like%20the%20C-17%2C%20are%20already%20flying%20beyond%20their%20originally