een%20growing%20crops%20like%20paddy%2C%20pearl%20millet%2C%20sorghum%2C%20and%20wheat.%20Despite%20toiling%20hard%20on%20the%20field%2C%20they%20would%20not%20get%20sufficient%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20entirely%20dependent%20on%20rainwater%20for%20irrigation%2C%20as%20the%20nearest%20river%20was%20four%20kilometres%20away%2C%20and%20we%20lacked%20the%20necessary%20machinery%20for%20lift%20irrigation.%20Consequently%2C%20our%20crops%20often%20dried%20up.%20Despite%20having%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20land%2C%20it%20remained%20barren%20for%20much%20of%20the%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20four%20was%20dependent%20on%20their%20father%E2%80%99s%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20and%20lived%20in%20a%20small%20%3Cem%3Ekachha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mud)%20home.%20Such%20was%20the%20financial%20status%20of%20the%20family%20that%20they%20survived%20on%20low-quality%20sorghum%20%3Cem%3Echapatis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flatbread)%2C%20and%20occasionally%2C%20vegetables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20Class%2010%2C%20Hrushikesh%20never%20wore%20a%20pair%20of%20slippers.%20At%2020%2C%20to%20supplement%20his%20family%20income%20and%20support%20his%20higher%20education%2C%20he%20started%20working%20for%20a%20marketing%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20job%2C%20I%20would%20receive%20Rs%203%2C500%20a%20month%20if%20I%20met%20the%20target%20of%20promoting%20Rs%201%20lakh%20in%20sales.%20This%20income%20was%20not%20fixed%2C%20and%20they%20required%20me%20to%20relocate%2025%20km%20away.%20I%20attempted%20to%20do%20this%20work%20for%20three%20to%20four%20months%2C%20but%20it%20became%20unsustainable%20because%20I%20also%20had%20to%20manage%20my%20field%20responsibilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F20